fixsource:fix-test-java

Full name:

com.kryshchuk.maven.plugins:fixsource-maven-plugin:1.1.3:fix-test-java

Description:

(no description)

Attributes:

  • Requires a Maven project to be executed.
  • The goal is thread-safe and supports parallel builds.
  • Since version: 1.0.
  • Binds by default to the lifecycle phase: process-test-sources.
